      <textblock>
        Inclusion criteria:

          -  Irritable Bowel Syndrome

          -  English speaking

        Exclusion criteria:

          -  Chronic pain condition other than Irritable Bowel Syndrome

          -  Medical condition that would contraindicate use of lidocaine

          -  Clinical criteria for fibromyalgia

          -  Presence of systemic disease such as diabetes, thyroid, gastrointestinal or liver
             disease, collagen vascular disease, malignancy, focal or neurological

          -  Seropositive HIV

          -  Pregnancy
